'''Turaga Sundara Rama Prasada Rao''' (born 1939) is an Indian engineer, known for his contributions in the fields of [[petroleum refining]] and [[heterogeneous catalysis]]. He is a former director of the [[Indian Institute of Petroleum]]<ref name="Life Time Achievement Award for Dr. T.S.R. Prasada Rao">{{Cite web |url=http://www.psuconnect.in/news/life-time-achievement-award-for-dr.-t.s.r.-prasada-rao/2347 |title=Life Time Achievement Award for Dr. T.S.R. Prasada Rao |date=2018-11-28 |website=PSUConnect |language=en-US |access-date=2018-11-28}}</ref> and a former deputy general manager of the [[Indian Petrochemicals Corporation Limited]].<ref name="Profile on Sarasijam">{{Cite web |url=http://www.sarasijam.com/docs/Prasada%20Rao%20Sarasijam%20Chairman%20Bio%20Jan%202009.pdf |title=Profile on Sarasijam |date=2018-11-28 |website=Sarasijam |access-date=2018-11-28}}</ref> He is known to have done studies in petrochemical engineering; his studies have been documented by way of a number of articles{{Refn|group=note|Please see ''Selected bibliography'' section}} and [[Google Scholar]], an online repository of scientific articles has listed 123 of them.<ref name="T.S.R. Prasada Rao - Google Scholar Citations">{{Cite web |url=https://scholar.google.co.in/citations?user=DZvRXxMAAAAJ&hl=en |title=T.S.R. Prasada Rao - Google Scholar Citations |date=2018-11-28 |website=scholar.google.co.in |access-date=2018-11-28}}</ref> He has also co-edited a book, ''Recent Advances in Basic and Applied Aspects of Industrial Catalysis'', published by [[Elsevier]].<ref name="RaoDhar1998">{{cite book|author1=T.S.R. Prasada Rao|author2=G. Murali Dhar|title=Recent Advances in Basic and Applied Aspects of Industrial Catalysis|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-zLl55UWDI0C|date=25 February 1998|publisher=Elsevier|isbn=978-0-08-054038-2}}</ref>

Born on January 20, 1939, Rao is an elected fellow of [[Indian National Academy of Engineering]],<ref name="Search for Fellow INAE">{{Cite web |url=https://inae.in/search-for-fellow/ |title=Search for Fellow INAE |date=2018-11-28 |website=Indian National Academy of Engineering (INAE) |language=en-US |access-date=2018-11-28}}</ref> and the [[Indian Academy of Sciences]].<ref name="Fellowship - Indian Academy of Sciences">{{Cite web |url=https://www.ias.ac.in/describe/fellow/Prasada_Rao,_Dr_Turaga_Sundara_Rama |title=Fellowship - Indian Academy of Sciences |date=2018-11-28 |language=en}}</ref> He is also a member of Andhra Pradesh Akademi of Sciences, [[Indian Institute of Chemical Engineers]], and [[New York Academy of Sciences]]. He shared the 1996 [[Om Prakash Bhasin Award]] for Engineering with [[M. R. Srinivasan]] and [[C. G. Krishnadas Nair]].<ref name="Engineering - OM PRAKASH BHASIN AWARDS">{{Cite web |url=http://www.opbfawards.com/engineering.html |title=Engineering - OM PRAKASH BHASIN AWARDS |date=2018-11-28 |website=www.opbfawards.com |access-date=2018-11-28}}</ref> He received the Petrotech Lifetime Achivement Award in 2004.<ref name="Dr. Rao Receives Lifetime Achievement Award - GTC Technology US, LLC">{{Cite web |url=http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:http://www.gtctech.com/dr-rao-receives-lifetime-achievement-award/ |title=Dr. Rao Receives Lifetime Achievement Award - GTC Technology US, LLC |date=2014-01-28 |website=GTC Technology US, LLC |access-date=2018-11-28}}</ref> He is also a recipient of several other honors including Chemtech Outstanding Scientist Award, K. G. Naik Gold Medal, [[FICCI]] Award Technology Award of the [[Council of Scientific and Industrial Research]].<ref name="Profile on Sarasijam" />

